node.text:
I've always found indulging in a sumptuous meal a worthy escape from the humdrum travails of millennial life. 

Here, I've got some basmati rice with a generous helping of salad and some amazing Thai curry. Prawns, basa, all the lovely meats to enhance your gastronomical fantasies, right in a bowl. 🍚🥘🍤🐟

Pictures can't do justice to conveying post-meal nirvana that's taken over me. Bliss. 😇

Figured I should make productive use of my last day of vacation before returning to the daily corporate grind. Here's my take on mac 'n cheese 🧀 with shrooms 🍄 & roasted cauli 🍽. On the side, some heavenly tuna 🐟 cutlets to devour on a wintry Sunday afternoon. 🌤
